{"tid":1035135,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿被限制推廣產品 台灣天王吳宗憲揚言發動藝人退出FB「我們可以去微信、抖音等其他同性質軟體繼續經營，絕對可以反制！」","createTime":"2019-02-24T12:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T12:20:40.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"017bce944a438389b6e8cdf6ccf3ae215faa2bee","tid":1035135,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"56歲台灣藝人吳宗憲稱霸綜藝界多年，雖然如此，但吳宗憲亦無故步自封，在這個網絡化的年代，吳宗憲於Facebook坐擁200萬Fans，更時常於FB推銷各項商品。不過最近FB更改系統制度，影響他收益，吳宗憲對此表示：「我們就是樹大招風嘛，我本來臉書（Facebook）直播都有1、2萬人，被限制頻寬後，竟然只剩3、4千人，所謂槍打出頭鳥，這家公司根本沒有contents（內容），所有內容來自網友，大家互為表裏，共生共榮，不應該限制任何人的直播或發文！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1550979797_7abd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1550979797_7abd.jpg&h=0058e458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日前吳宗憲大罵Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n日前吳宗憲大罵Facebook，對制度改變影響收入大為不滿，更表示：「雖然臉書亞洲區這些主管很多是我好友，但他們只能坐領高薪，仰人鼻息，還是得聽命老外，若超越界線，這樣繼續限制我們，我將發動飛彈營的藝人、名人們退出臉書，我們可以去微信、TikTok（抖音）等其他同性質軟體繼續經營，絕對可以反制！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TgrPAJ5TU5DfXKQtYt_Rqg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/entertainment.nownews.hk/c4e9a8fea91d98d1e115b8e08e7446ab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTgrPAJ5TU5DfXKQtYt_Rqg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2Fc4e9a8fea91d98d1e115b8e08e7446ab&h=7c8af4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBTZ6u0.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=1004&amp;y=259\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBTZ6u0.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D1004%26y%3D259&h=494d00bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳宗憲對於臉書限制多多相當生氣。<br />\n<br />\n吳宗憲表示，有部份合作商家會因應Facebook要求付費，每付一次FB會將內容派送給更多的人，但他痛批：「我們又沒有任何違法或傷風敗俗的行為，也是合法在繳稅，如果他們只賣頻寬也太沒格調！他們如果限制我，所有人不會坐視。」他還呼籲FB「不要當一隻驕縱的大象，螞蟻雄兵一直都有行動的。」"},{"pid":"8079a2cf49a63d12a4120712b938dc03effa2a48","tid":1035135,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c43ef87c9d2d43b4ad32116fb95c8893fae6af","tid":1035135,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"fb打壓d page迫你落廣告都唔係今時今日嘅事,佢咁玩法其實係迫走晒會掉錢落你度嘅客d cooperate 客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10810802759cc82a56fca0619d4183a4ea035a84","tid":1035135,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"仲有人用FB架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}